**File or folder** — Box API [Add collaboration to an item](https://developer.box.com/reference/post-collaborations). Uses `target_type` `file` or `folder` with `target_id`. Allowed `role` values: `editor`, `viewer`, `previewer`, `uploader`, `previewer uploader`, `viewer uploader` (`co-owner` is not permitted via this tool). Optional `notify` controls email notification. `can_view_path` is only valid for **folder** targets.

